title: a-ha +T. Schumacher vs. Fredrika2--Celice (Way out there remix)
description:
As I promised (threatened?), here is the remix of the fairly recent a-ha song Celice. Using a friend&#039;s wonderful gadgets, I&#039;ve taken the fine remix done by Thomas Schumacher and turned it into something way out there: a 13 minute piece to make you want to tear your hair, perhaps. Well, it&#039;s all done for fun. Used instruments and virtual instruments include 

White Noise Audio Doppelmangler
Korg M1
Hartmann Neuron
Quantum Leap East West Symphonic Choir
Zero-G Analogue Sequencer Loops VSTi
Zero-G Altered States VSTi
my Daisy Rock electric guitar
Native Instruments Guitar Rig 2

mp3@192kbps
